{"tid":2014457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"汶川地震12周年 家長悼活埋學生 公安踩場","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T05:30:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2cae7f3e2ac63ba4a334c0000c7aebad42d6be","tid":2014457,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200513/TJL3OCQPHRJK3UJGZZ7LLFHYJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200513%2FTJL3OCQPHRJK3UJGZZ7LLFHYJQ%2F&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9Ndw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=834a7155\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200513%2FTJL3OCQPHRJK3UJGZZ7LLFHYJQ%2F&h=fe833ac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200513/TJL3OCQPHRJK3UJGZZ7LLFHYJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n汶川地震12周年<br />\n家長悼活埋學生 公安踩場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200513/large/1589300193_7abd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200513%2Flarge%2F1589300193_7abd.gif&h=6736c5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一批家長在都江堰悼念在地震中喪生的子女。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨天是汶川5．12地震12周年，北川、都江堰等地有家長自發集體悼念，部份人稱當局派公安便衣在場監視，禁止他們掛橫額，亦打爛搭建的花壇等。曾調查豆腐渣校舍工程的異見人士譚作人，在地震紀念前「被旅遊」，不准留在四川，也不能接受傳媒訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚作人被迫外遊禁受訪<br />\n<br />\n下午2時28分，地震發生的一刻，官方安排網上祭奠儀式，並在北川老縣城地震遺址直播。不過當年曾就豆腐渣校舍發起公。。。。。。。。。。政權罪」判處五年徒刑，2014年獲釋後，多年來仍持續受到監視。<br />\n<br />\n當年有逾278名學生喪生的都江堰聚源中學，上下午均有家長到場悼念子女，在遺址附近擺放花壇。但有家長指，每個路。。。。。。。。。。公安理論，亦有人將未被丟爛的鮮花插在路邊，擺放食品拜祭及在路邊燒冥鏹。<br />\n<br />\n北川中學當年有一千餘名師生被活埋遇難，是地震中死傷最慘重的學校。昨有過百名家長到遺址悼念。家長向媽對本報。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。淡忘，我們怎麼能忘呢？」她又稱，每年因豆腐渣校舍問題上訪，和其他家長約定「只要尚有一口氣，都會上訪」。"},{"pid":"72456b2685f502117c257597bb204193edf46937","tid":2014457,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"香港拜下周同學一樣有公安踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c90f260f9ebde68ff41f2746b6315a0fb5db2e9","tid":2014457,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72456b2685f502117c257597bb204193edf46937","tid":2014457,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"香港拜下周同學一樣有公安踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"一制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\