79e7d3fa12e8f909d68aa222d52cc2a79","tid":2014457,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"支持公安執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa1070788ae03b14fd494adace827c240eb003a","tid":2014457,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"又出黎搞事 一定收左美國錢"},{"pid":"94d647d6aa97911b62be3eeceb87080d388a8f65","tid":2014457,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"假家屬丫嘛"},{"pid":"3aeedca00f165bf0510d0aa18f350ac633bdee57","tid":2014457,"uid":2567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"江城子&middot;廢墟下的自述<br />\n<br />\n 一位廢墟中的地震遇難者，冥冥之中感知了地震之後地面上發生的一切，遂發出如是感慨&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n 天災難避死何訴，<br />\n<br />\n 主席喚，總理呼，<br />\n<br />\n 黨疼國愛，聲聲入廢墟。<br />\n<br />\n 十三億人共一哭，<br />\n<br />\n 縱做鬼，也幸福。<br />\n<br />\n 銀鷹戰車救雛犢，<br />\n<br />\n 左軍叔，右警姑，<br />\n<br />\n 民族大愛，親歷死也足。<br />\n<br />\n 只盼墳前有屏幕，<br />\n<br />\n 看奧運，同歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}